<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Performance</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>~0.6<sp/>microseconds<sp/>per<sp/>evaluation<sp/>(simple<sp/>expressions)</highlight></codeline>
