<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>implementation<sp/>demonstrates<sp/>that<sp/>apertures<sp/>can<sp/>serve<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>practical<sp/>security<sp/>primitive<sp/>for<sp/>distributed<sp/>computation,<sp/>enabling<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>class<sp/>of<sp/>privacy-preserving<sp/>applications.</highlight></codeline>
